overview: Raden Mas Panji Komeng has a unique habit of eating crackers. Everyone in his organisation, including his beautiful personal secretary, strongly supports Raden Mas Panji Komeng, including the sexy, Jupe, even though she already has a boyfriend. One day, Komeng meets Jojon who is tackling a gang of criminals about to rob Komeng’s house. Jojon works as a security guard. His colleagues don’t care for him except for Lia, who admires him.
title: Mau Dong... Ah
